<div style="background-color: #f8f8f8; padding: 20px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">
    <div style="background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 8px; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: left;">
        <h2 style="text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Email Confirmation</h2>
        <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
        <p>Thank you for creating an account with Eislett. Please use the following confirmation code to verify your email address:</p>
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; white-space: nowrap;">
            <!-- Start of code loop -->
            {{#each code}}
                <span style="display: inline-block; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 4px; padding: 10px; margin: 0 2px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; width: 30px; text-align: center; background-color: #f0f0f0;">{{this}}</span>
            {{/each}}
            <!-- End of code loop -->
        </div>
        <p>If you did not create an account, please ignore this email or contact our support team.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>Eislett Team</p>
    </div>
</div>